



Export settings for NLA Animation:

select armature and mesh
export FBX
selected objects, apply transform, meshandarmatureonly,check/uncheck NLA in animation tab
make sure shield is in for all actions

in Unity, drag to scene, add animator, add animation controller and point object animator to controller


Attach bone to curve:

Make a bone constraint in pose mode in the last bone in the chain. point it to the curve after ensuring that the number of bones matches teh number of control points on the curve (usually vertices divided by 3.

add ample geometry and set all object origins to starting point of curve.


Set rest position

